---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Therapist for Berkeley Residents | EMDR & Anxiety | Maren Voss"
  description="Oakland-based therapist minutes from Berkeley. Specializing in EMDR, trauma, anxiety, and burnout. In-person and telehealth available."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="interior-hero section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="heading-page">Therapist for Berkeley Residents</h1>
      <p class="interior-hero__tagline">Oakland-based, five minutes from downtown Berkeley.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>If you're looking for a therapist in or near Berkeley, my office in Rockridge is a short trip across the Oakland-Berkeley border. The office is one block from Rockridge BART, making it accessible from anywhere on the BART line.</p>
        <p>Many of my Berkeley clients are affiliated with UC Berkeley or the graduate programs at CIIS, the Wright Institute, or GTU. I understand the specific pressures of academic life: the publish-or-perish mentality, the imposter syndrome that comes with being surrounded by high-caliber peers, and the way institutional culture can demand performance while offering very little support.</p>
        <p>I also work with Berkeley residents who are in tech, healthcare, nonprofit work, or any field where the demands are high and the internal pressure to keep producing is relentless. If you're in Berkeley and searching for a therapist who specializes in EMDR, anxiety, trauma, or burnout, I'd be glad to talk.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>I specialize in <a href="/trauma-ptsd" class="text-link-dark">trauma & PTSD</a>, <a href="/anxiety" class="text-link-dark">anxiety</a>, <a href="/burnout" class="text-link-dark">burnout and high-achiever stress</a>, <a href="/relationship-patterns" class="text-link-dark">relationship patterns</a>, and <a href="/life-transitions" class="text-link-dark">life transitions</a>. My approach integrates EMDR, IFS, and somatic therapy.</p>
        <p><a href="/how-i-work" class="text-link-dark">Learn more about how I work &rarr;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="geo-info">
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Office</h2>
          <p>5432 College Ave, Suite 204, Oakland, CA 94618</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">From Berkeley</h2>
          <p>5-10 minutes by car, one BART stop from downtown Berkeley (Rockridge station)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Telehealth</h2>
          <p>Available for all California residents. If commuting isn't convenient, video sessions are a full alternative.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Getting Started</h2>
          <p><a href="/contact" class="text-link-light">Schedule a free 15-minute consultation &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .interior-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--section-pad) + 72px);
  }

  .interior-hero__tagline {
    color: var(--text-muted-light);
    font-size: var(--body);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .body-text p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .body-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .geo-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px 64px;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .geo-info__item h2 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .geo-info__item p {
    font-size: var(--body-small);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .geo-info {
      gap: 40px 48px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .geo-info {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
